name: Uyen Trang Nguyen
content: Professor Uyen Trang Nguyen - York University Uyen Trang Nguyen - Associate Professor Thank you for visiting my home page. I am an associate professor at York University, Lassonde School of Engineering, Department of Electrical Engineering & Computer Science. I am affiliated with the Computer Networks & Security Lab and Security Research at York (SecRAY). I received my Bachelor of Computer Science degree and Master of Computer Science degree from Concordia University (Montreal, Canada). I completed my Ph.D. degree at the University of Toronto (Toronto, Canada) in 2003, under the supervision of Drs. Kenneth C. Sevcik and Irene Katzela. From 1995 to 1997 I was a software developer at Nortel Networks (Montreal, Canada). I joined York University in 2002.
